HEADWORD: Sphyraenoid
<hw>Sphy*rae"noid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos><ety>[L.
<ets>sphyraena</ets> a kind of sea fish (Gr. <grk>sfy`raina</grk>) +
<ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the
